Name: Amped Up
Description: Come meet the brothers of Nu Delta at our beautiful Boston 4 story mansion. Stick around and get house tours, play some video games, pool, fuse ball, and much more. Challenge and defeat the most brothers and you'll walk away with a fabulous prize!

Name: Southern Style Chicken
Description: Tomorrow's gonna be a long day. Take it easy tonight with the brothers of Nu Delta and enjoy some southern style chicken and relax before our action packed Sunday filled with activities you do NOT want to miss!

Name: JET SKIS
Description: An afternoon on the beach, Jet Skiing, and Nu Delt bros? Doesn't get much better than that!

Name: Paintball
Description: An evening of indoor painball right before the Party Bus is a great start to a looong night!

Name: Night Rider
Description: Event name says it all. Hop on and learn why our party bus has been a Nu Delta exclusive event for many years.

Name: Firing Range
Description: Test your aim with a set of different rifles and handguns. Beginner or expert, this is a thrilling (and safe) event for everyone

Name: SkyZone
Description: Your backyard trampoline has nothing on this experience. Dodgeball, basketball, back flips and more!

Name: Steak & Lobster
Description: Prime steak and fresh caught lobster. A hearty meal is definitely a necessity before Monster Jam tonight!

Name: MONSTER JAM
Description: Come see how the brothers of Nu Delta get down and find out why our parties are repetitively sponsored by Monster. You've waited all day for this, trust us.

Name: Target Runs
Description: We'll take 2 separate trips to Target to make sure we all have all the supplies for the coming semester. Give us a call for a ride.

Name: Roofdeck BBQ
Description: Come chill and kick back on the day before classes with the brothers of Nu Delta. Enjoy good music and an epic view of the Charles River and Cambridge from high up Boston on the Nu Delta rooftop.

Name: Dick's Last Resort
Description: Things get pretty rowdy whenever Nu Delts show up to Dick's Last Resort. Take a night out to celebrate your first classes at MIT!

Name: SK Late Night
Description: Come down to Sigma Kappa and watch ND throw down in a talent show against some of the other MIT fraternities!  It's always a great show, so make sure not to miss it!

Name: Relay for Life
Description: Every year the brothers make sure to show their support for the fight against cancer by joining many other MIT and Wellesley students in a relay for life.  All proceeds made in the event are directed towards groundbreaking research in every type of cancer that could save many lives.  So come by and support the cause with us!  You can sign up <a href = '
://www.relayforlife.org/index'>here.

Name: The D is far Dance
Description: Come challenge the brothers of Nu Delta to Just Dance! Food and drink will be served.

Name: ND Lounging
Description: Want to party tonight? We'll be ready to party hop with you. Or maybe you'd just like to take the night off until the real party at Nu Delta tomorrow(SIKE, not happening anymore)? Either way, come meet and chill with the brothers of Nu Delta at our house. There will be delicious chicken wings, good music, games, and more to go round!

Name: Tex-Mex Breakast
Description: Swing by Nu Delta for an amazing Tex-Mex style breakfast with chorizo & eggs, chilaquiles, and breakfast tacos/burritos. And BACON!!!

Name: Rock Bed Barbecue
Description: Nothing beats a good burger on a Saturday afternoon on Nu Delta's iconic Phoenix Rock Garden. Come enjoy some great music and meet the brothers of Nu Delta.

Name: Interfraternal Bash
Description: PARTY HARDY

Name: Nu Smoothies
Description: All partied out tonight? Looking for something to eat? Stop by Nu Delta on your way home to close out the night with snacks and some next level smoothies.

Name: Breakfast of Champions
Description: Rise From The Ashes of last night's parties with a Breakfast Of Champions at Nu Delta. 460 Beacon ST. Guaranteed to be delicious.
